Package us.pserver.revok.container

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CredentialsSource
    Represents a source of Credentials objects.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Authenticator
    Execute authentications of Credentials objects against a CredentialsSource database.
    Credentials
    The Credentials object encapsulates information about username, password and namespace access for authentication with the server.
    ListCredentialsSource
    A CredentialsSource based on a list of Credentials objects.
    ObjectContainer
    Objects container on server, biding them to a recovery String key.
    SingleCredentialsSource
    A CredentialsSource based on a single Credentials object.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    AuthenticationException
    Represents an error in the authentication process on the server.
